pq_gfwFJE-eUaBTbxRUjnlA9bdtrM4kI9PGQL0GrmFQ&oe=6771245D"}, {"file_name": "Soccer5e.png", "id": "830763342466078", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57572940_830763345799411_4192181376620077197_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wkbsSzopCg8Q7kNvgHNtVB9&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAoLmA8l65lbl7tK5NaSj-9HJ8Ji4WkMOUuh7wLe81laQ&oe=67711E7B"}, {"file_name": "zerog5e.png", "id": "1048405573450539", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001714_1048405576783872_3723899864187407035_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2w6wsNdXlOMQ7kNvgGePTdk&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBmtp8F9F7xCX7nLgsbpbzUUW3IbEtR1hDgHk7B1ltOtA&oe=677138FB"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "vIDEOcOVETR.png", "id": "8964806610218356", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974646_8964806620218355_1338032258312468621_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=w3N89nM_8uEQ7kNvgEV0an7&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA-ucf6731ZtbgIjgXLdjSUVb4teEzljaR7s77qXI3wSQ&oe=677147EA"}, "display_name": "Banana Company", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Banana.Co is a fun and engaging virtual reality game where players embody bananas in a whimsical world. Inspired by Gorilla Tag mechanics, it offers a lighthearted adventure perfect for those aged 13 and up. We welcome everyone as long as they practice safe gaming.\n\nCommunity Guidelines: Our inclusive community prioritizes enjoyment and respect. A dedicated moderation team ensures a safe and friendly environment.\n\nGameplay Features: Explore imaginative maps, customize your banana with various cosmetics, and engage in creative activities. Players can forge friendships and enjoy lively interactions.\n\nJoin us in Banana.Co for a unique experience that celebrates fun, creativity, and camaraderie in a world of laughter!\n[Yellow44 is watching]", "short_descripti